name: std::<process::Child as core::fmt::Debug>::fmt
src:
fn fmt(&self, f: &mut fmt::Formatter<'_>) -> fmt::Result {
        f.debug_struct("Child")
            .field("stdin", &self.stdin)
            .field("stdout", &self.stdout)
            .field("stderr", &self.stderr)
            .finish_non_exhaustive()
    }
